    <h1>FRS 102 Revenue Recognition — Is It Squeezing Your Recovery Rates?</h1>
    <p class="standfirst">The amendments apply from January 2026, but the admin burden is already here. Here's what the revenue recognition changes mean for your bookkeeping and your recovery rates.</p>
  </div>
